   <abstract>In the recto, this post card shows Jack Dalton with a guitar on the left of the card and a horse named "Prince" on the right of the card. Verso reads: Hello There Radio Friends ! I hope you like this new Colorphoto of me and my horse "Prince." Many thanks for your swell cards and letters. Sincerly, Jack Dalton, "Radio's Original Singing Cowboy" WBZ--Boston.</abstract>
